query:
SELECT 
  pwi.id as wave_item_id,
  pwi.productName,
  pwi.batch,
  pr.pickingOrderId,
  po.customerOrderNumber
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
JOIN inventory inv ON (
  pwi.locationId = inv.locationId 
  AND pwi.productId = inv.productId 
  AND COALESCE(pwi.batch, '') = COALESCE(inv.batch, '')
)
JOIN pickingReservations pr ON inv.id = pr.inventoryId
JOIN pickingOrders po ON pr.pickingOrderId = po.id
WHERE pwi.waveId = 30004
GROUP BY pwi.id, pwi.productName, pwi.batch, pr.pickingOrderId, po.customerOrderNumber;
